{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-419-look-and-say-sequence","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 419: mfululizo wa tazama na sema","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sekvenca 'Gledaj i reci' počinje sa 1, 11, 21, 1211, 111221, 312211, 13112221, 1113213211, ...</p>\n<p>Niz počinje brojem 1, a svaki sledeći član dobija se opisivanjem prethodnog člana uzastopnim brojevima.</p>\n<p>Inasaidia kusema haya kwa sauti:</p>\n<p>1 je 'moja moja' $→ 11$</p>\n<p>11 ni 'mbili moja' $→ 21$</p>\n<p>21 je 'moja mbili na moja moja' $→ 1211$</p>\n<p>1211 ni 'moja moja, moja mbili na mbili moja' $→ 111221$</p>\n<p>111221 je 'tri jedan, dva dva i jedan jedan' $→ 312211$</p>\n<p>...</p>\n<p>Definisati $A(n)$, $B(n)$ i $C(n)$ kao brojeve jedan, dva i tri u $n$-tom članu sekvence respektivno. Može se dokazati da $A(40) = 31\\,254$, $B(40) = 20\\,259$ i $C(40) = 11\\,625$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $A(n)$, $B(n)$ i $C(n)$ za $n = {10}^{12}$. Navedi svoj odgovor modulo $2^{30}$ kao niz znakova i navedi svoje vrednosti za $A$, $B$ i $C$ koristeći zarez kao separator. Primer, za $n = 40$ odgovor će biti <code>31254,20259,11625</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5101000cf542c510022","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302088,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-419-look-and-say-sequence"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function lookAndSaySequence() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nlookAndSaySequence();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB"